{"id": 2798, "genre": 1001, "title": "你并不喜欢什么样的「好人」？", "description": "啥事都想大事化小小事化了的和事佬什么的，总想和这样的人保持一段距离。", "record_count": 3840, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/20190218170439vFMwfIlmPBDnOaCh.jpg", "page_style": 0, "category": 2, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "2019-02-21T03:00:00Z", "options": [{"id": 328704, "content": "说“差不多就行了”的差不多先生", "image": null, "praise_count": 6, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1110856}, {"id": 328960, "content": "都可以，没关系，啥都行，你喜欢，迁就你", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1444550}, {"id": 328705, "content": "还没搞清楚状况就开喷的人", "image": null, "praise_count": 15, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1429344}, {"id": 329217, "content": "我自己吧", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1327094}, {"id": 328706, "content": "“我是为你好”\n\n然后将我推入无尽的地狱", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1590305}, {"id": 328707, "content": "两面派的", "image": null, "praise_count": 7, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1475387}, {"id": 328708, "content": "中央空调", "image": null, "praise_count": 11, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1198027}, {"id": 328709, "content": "因为别人的不同的选则而去强行纠正人的三观的自认为三观很正的人。", "image": null, "praise_count": 6, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1412144}, {"id": 328710, "content": "一定要强调为对方付出了什么", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1587459}, {"id": 328711, "content": "伪好人", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1021734}, {"id": 328713, "content": "自己受尽委屈各种忍耐妥协，但私下里又来抱怨吐槽，大多都是“没办法只能这样”的话，这种好人蛮多的但是挺累的希望能刚一点不然很容易被欺负吧", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1590319}, {"id": 328714, "content": "“吃啥”？“随便啊”的好人。", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1272598}, {"id": 328716, "content": "讨厌打着“我都是为你好”却不断干涉别人人生的人", "image": null, "praise_count": 10, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1590328}, {"id": 328718, "content": "我都是为了你好💀", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1587806}, {"id": 329742, "content": "当面对你好的人", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1595636}, {"id": 328719, "content": "不了解事情原委，就劝你大度，算了吧的那种所谓的好人，奇葩！", "image": null, "praise_count": 10, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1590351}, {"id": 328720, "content": "自己的权益被侵犯了也不敢站出来发声一句就算了吧就解决问题了", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1514757}, {"id": 328721, "content": "闲着瞎操心的人，让人烦。", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1590352}, {"id": 329746, "content": "所谓的“老师”", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1595652}, {"id": 328723, "content": "Ta还是个孩子", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1579137}, {"id": 334867, "content": "没什么", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1298793}, {"id": 328724, "content": "只会拍领导马屁完全服从领导 成为领导眼中好人的好人 🤮🙄", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1590369}, {"id": 329238, "content": "总是怀念过去，活在过去的人。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1106338}, {"id": 328727, "content": "你真是个好人……", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1590384}, {"id": 328728, "content": "我这么说这么做都是为了你好的好人", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1393355}, {"id": 330008, "content": "什么事都和他有关系一定要掺和一脚", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1596793}, {"id": 329241, "content": "发生什么事情都让人看开点", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1593558}, {"id": 329499, "content": "后人曲解 论语  的弊端之一", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1594711}, {"id": 328733, "content": "工作的时候，告诉新人偷懒的”技巧”。", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1113490}, {"id": 328735, "content": "杠精", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1576208}, {"id": 328736, "content": "具体情况都不了解，张口就来“算了吧”。明明场合气氛不对，还给你拆台，“大家以和为贵，不要吵”，一点立场都没有，这样的和稀泥水平太差了", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1590422}, {"id": 328992, "content": "强行撮合婚姻的媒婆", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1591332}, {"id": 328737, "content": "不是好人的好人。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1244139}, {"id": 328739, "content": "“宝贝儿你好棒 你好厉害（白眼”", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1588525}, {"id": 328740, "content": "自己", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 596413}, {"id": 329252, "content": "慷他人之慨的见了早远离", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1543054}, {"id": 328741, "content": "无论你发表什么观点，他总想表达的比你更牛逼😭杠精真的很烦诶", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1590442}, {"id": 328743, "content": "没有主见，“我都行”", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1465565}, {"id": 328744, "content": "追求时被人说“你是好人”", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1032011}, {"id": 330024, "content": "嘴上说着无所谓，表现的很佛系。实际还想使无脑绊子的傻子。", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1595767}, {"id": 328745, "content": "看到别人的错误不仅不纠正，还鼓励的人。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1566428}, {"id": 328746, "content": "麻烦你帮个忙", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1555854}, {"id": 328748, "content": "好人", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1436833}, {"id": 328749, "content": "以考验你抗压能力为由降薪酬的领导。", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1480549}, {"id": 337197, "content": "跟每一个人的关系都很好", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1626912}, {"id": 328750, "content": "“都行，都行”", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1338462}, {"id": 329009, "content": "自己觉得自己特帅，特牛逼，特有钱，其实就是个没见过世面的傻子 \n", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1591382}, {"id": 328754, "content": "我跟他说话，他好像听不见", "image": null, "praise_count": 8, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 529205}, {"id": 328755, "content": "自负的人", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 205508}, {"id": 328756, "content": "不要损害自己的利益 去讨好别人", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1355710}]}